com.team6.project.dao

Interface OperatorCountryDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JPAOperatorCountryDAO

    public interface OperatorCountryDAO
    Operator Country data access object.

    Handles database interactions for OperatorCountry related functionality. This is primarily CRUD operations as this object behaves as a reference table.

    Author:
    John O Keeffe, Eoin Kernan, James Mc Ternan
